						<p>I liked it &#8211; it wasn&#8217;t immediately obvious and made you think [well, made me think].  I also liked how there could be different interpretations of what the writer is trying to gain from the letter or the situation with Mr Charles and his death.</p>
<p>It seems very time I read it, I come up with something else.  Great stuff!</p>
