						<p>Glad you liked it &#8211; yeah keeping the motivation about explanation with the bad language (and a natural tendency to mock the great white English imperialists) proved challenging.<br />
I thought this would be an easy idea to write but had a lot of trouble getting it short enough and still all there.</p>
